ygData.messageBody:
Nah, then everyone could do tham and be warmly to Antonican Bard Guilds.
More likely you get a mandolin or flute (of the normal variety) for killing
some fire drakes or some such thing.

By Erolissi I hope not. Please do not let it be so. Guess I'll try to get
my poor little test bard thru Nek forest to find out. <Shiver>

Kitasi
